Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:05.23,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.56,0:00:09.94,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalalalalala
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.32,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}やあ また会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.70,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ねぇ こんばんは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.62,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}いや こんにちはだって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.16,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}広いようで 狭いようで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.87,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}退屈はいらないみたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:23.75,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}あぁ 問題は依然あって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.79,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}頭痛いんだけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:28.21,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}少しずつって言い聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.38,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}願い事叶えて行きましょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:35.43,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}I shall remember I wanna do I shall remember
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:41.27,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}拾い集めた後悔のかけらたちを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:43.52,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}夜が明ける前に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:47.52,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何遍を貼って 並べてて 希望に変える
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.07,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}10秒継続中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:54.07,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}桜が去つて散ったその後で
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:57.87,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}何が真実なのかは かるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:01.70,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody そう今は奏でて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:06.62,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}愛が世界救うのだなんて 僕は信じてないけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:12.30,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今 目の前の君が 明日を生きれるくらいには
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:13.59,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:16.09,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不条理は吹き飛ばしていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.39,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀楽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:20.85,opjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}大丈夫さ　どこまでもゆくだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:26.31,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}All quartets lead to the? lalalala　lalalalalala!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:21.09,edch,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.32,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呀啊 又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.40,0:00:13.70,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}呐 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.70,0:00:15.62,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不 应该是中午好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.62,0:00:18.16,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}好像很宽敞 又好像很拥挤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.16,0:00:20.87,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过貌似和「无聊」二字无缘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:23.75,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}啊 问题依然还在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.79,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}真是让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:28.21,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不过还是向我慢慢道来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:31.38,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我们一起去实现愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.09,0:00:41.27,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将散落一地的后悔的碎片小心收起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:43.52,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在天明之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.69,0:00:47.52,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}一遍遍地粘合 一遍遍地重排 将之变为希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:50.07,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}持续10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:54.07,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在那满树樱花逝去之后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:57.87,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}什么才是真实 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.87,0:01:01.70,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}future melody 没错 现在就奏响吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:06.62,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}都说爱会拯救世界 我可一点都不信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.13,0:01:12.30,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}现在 眼前的你 想要享受明天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:13.59,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:16.09,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}先把不合理统统打飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.39,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}with 喜怒哀乐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:20.85,opch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}放心吧 我们无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.36,0:01:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,能去提醒一下那只「觉」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,少给我用广域读心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我比其他人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵好使很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.50,0:01:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微有一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.12,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要说你自己去说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,用你那「借」来的觉的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,倒也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不过借来的毕竟是借来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不能很好地控制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟这个才是我的本职
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,比泉家的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 就是比泉家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,比泉家的力量中 有表和里…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,即阴和阳之分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,宗家——你的力量是「调律」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是将物体送往对侧的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而分家的我是「堕化」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是从对侧拉回这里的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.80,0:02:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,两种力量都能让物体跨越次元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.59,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看来槙春真的什么都没告诉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,调律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.52,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么円神认识爷爷…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,问得好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不准读
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不准随便读别人的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单 我们见过面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那个世界…对面的世界?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,爷爷怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟送走槙春的人 就是秋名你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,话题扯远了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,回过头来说说宗家和分家为何拥有同样力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那是远在七乡出现之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至远在比泉円阳一家七口被送走那天之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,那时 人丁兴旺的比泉家中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只存在本家一家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也只有本家的长男拥有能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,某一年 本家期盼已久的男孩降生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,据说是非常健康的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但比泉家上下无不慌乱万分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,理由只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为降生的男孩是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,一人拥有送走之力 一人拥有带来之力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,力量一分为二的血统
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,分成了宗家和分家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.91,0:04:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们是宗家而我们是分家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.79,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为带来之力…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,堕化之力是这世上多余的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至可以说是被唾弃的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 言归正传
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,比泉秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,和我联手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,就算占据了你的身体 恐怕也无法完全获得宗家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 只要完美状态的你与我联手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就能轻松支配这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,支配人类 妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.45,0:05:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如何 光想想就很有趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,就算那样我也不会开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个交易对你没有任何好处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这不是提议 而是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但还有这种好处呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要支配了这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,任何人都要顺从你的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,看上的家伙可以随便作为奴隶放在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这个交易不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你动不动就出现 还没什么威严
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我有些太小瞧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这点我或许该道个歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看来没必要道歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.76,0:06:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你也太小瞧我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,给我下来 你这混账
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就把你打回那个世界去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,表情不错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细想来这还是第一次啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,能这样不受打扰地跟你单打独斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你的力量和我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的力量更强
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里分个高下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么点本事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好吗 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.89,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,每多用一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你的力量我大致了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,用得还行嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是很想拿这个给你最后一击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呀 不过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你把它调律掉我也不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的本事咯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,未成年人竟然这个时间外出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,云珠大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你找我校学生和毕业生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,有何贵干
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.98,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,元老院的走狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,要用擅长的阴阳道来试试阻止我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 这可难了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,阴阳道是枝垂的专业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我虽然差了一个水平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但也足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,阴阳道真是个不错的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是人类智慧的结晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你很从容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,确实有些蹊跷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.69,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,比我多用了这么多力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,却没有任何变化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这也实在太…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.03,0:08:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,从容过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这有些窍门的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我在与生俱来的才能中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微加了些理论知识
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼前那男的不就是个例子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,阴阳道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 给我理论的不是这个男的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,而是那个蓬头混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,枝垂那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,把阴阳道加入比泉家的力量中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,阴阳道归根结底
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是不依靠比泉家的力量 往来于次元之间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,并以此为根源的学问
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,能增幅堕化之力也合情合理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,仅仅明白了理论 怎么能立刻用于实践…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,按照以完美理论为基础的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,就算试行一百万次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,也只会带来同一个结果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.45,0:10:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,科学必须如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.62,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,理论?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,既然有这种东西 那我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,比泉家的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,理论还不够完美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这不过是…这不过是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.39,0:10:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,增幅比泉家力量的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,被送去那边的人如今怎样 你很想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.70,0:10:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,让你见见吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,给你叫来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…这…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不愿相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过算了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,最坏的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我还打算把那副身体连同力量一起占据掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要是这么死了就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别管了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,快一点 言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经最快了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,枪樱 交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,重死了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,要挡下来才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,来帮忙啦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧 桃华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哥…哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我们还在吵架呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 最讨厌哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,桃华…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉小姐 救命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,秋名他…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我帮不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.44,0:13:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,次元错位得好严重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好严重…这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,莉菈?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.92,0:13:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 花束…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,给客人惊喜让客人开心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我身为表演者的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要的不是感谢而是笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…还是谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,没兴致了 我还是撤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.89,0:14:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,熊好像也从林子里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啦 被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 也告诉了那家伙不少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉他对你有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,没好处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,只是让他知道真相并为此烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,罪恶感 猜疑心…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他能为这些东西感到痛苦就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.46,0:15:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 我一直有个疑惑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你也能用「调律」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对了 我以前让你看过呐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然分为了两派
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但力量并没有完全被一分为二
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.68,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 和宗家的力量比起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只能说聊胜于无吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙体内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,也沉睡着堕化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,记住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,将毁灭这个世界的怪物并不只是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,还有另外一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那时的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想成为魔法师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,向星星许了愿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,星星回应了我的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.35,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我接下了流星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都在注意着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我宝贵的妹妹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然会注意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 小阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,去巡逻前先诊查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,没精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,然后那边是因为和円神的决斗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,没分出胜负就结束了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,男孩子就是男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好 小阿姬结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是小秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我挠我挠我挠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,您这是干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.30,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,谁让你拉长着一张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,有道是笑门开幸福来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在女孩子面前一定要有笑容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,在有些消沉的女孩子面前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只有人类能通过握手救助秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,身为妖怪的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为…为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就算和我握手也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不能恢复调律的错位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不 这次最终也没让城市受到损害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你有注意流弹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这握手 是慰问你的辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 今天是秋日祭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,要回事务所准备一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢了 茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,回头见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有精神了没 小阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没那么容易
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才还那么消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,握个手就打起精神
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我才没有那么单纯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真是单纯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我也要去巡逻了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了 茱莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.47,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,又率直又开朗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她算是姐姐的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,她也就是我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想到将和她熟识起来 真让人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就是说 莉菈要住在这城市里咯?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只能帮帮小忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,超级欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,久疏问候了 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我还活着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 再见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好简洁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,只要活着怎么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是这个意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,莉菈 能帮我个忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬在消除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛 她的心情我理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.84,0:20:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今天天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,正适合庙会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这不很精神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.81,0:20:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,啊…啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有精神是好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.52,0:20:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,很好很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,据说三丁目有个老婆婆迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.19,0:21:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬…嗯…阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哇啊啊 阿姬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.70,0:21:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,阿姬被掳走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 莉菈小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.63,0:21:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出门办事顺便送你一程
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.17,0:21:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…啊咧?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,既然莉菈小姐是人类…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那把大剑…还有飞起来的医院…还有魔法扫把…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是魔术?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是怎么做到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然想知道魔术的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.73,0:21:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不能说这种不懂事的话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想看的话 随时都可以表演给各位看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没有机关也没有障眼法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:59.33,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.92,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}将时钟的指针拨反过来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.76,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在梦中轻轻啜泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:09.55,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}我又开始了今天的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:25.11,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}喜欢谈天说地却讨厌侧耳倾听
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:28.74,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}喜欢品尝美食却讨厌亲手烹调
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:32.37,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}能包容你如此任性的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:36.08,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}全世界就只有我一人 你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:39.75,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}这眼泪是为谁而流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.38,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}为我吗 亦或是为你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:47.09,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}流干眼泪之后又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:50.72,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}还是想和谁在一起吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:54.22,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.85,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}听我讲述昨夜的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.77,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}在这个破除了魔法的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.19,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}我四处搜寻着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:08.90,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.49,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}让我听一听你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:19.21,edch,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}再次将我带入甜美的梦乡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:59.33,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.92,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}时计の针を逆さまに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:04.76,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}梦に泣いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.76,0:22:09.55,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}今日もまた 仆は生きる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:25.11,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}おしゃべりがすき 闻くのはきらい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.11,0:22:28.74,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}食べることがすき 作るのはきらい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.74,0:22:32.37,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}そんなわがままが通じるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.41,0:22:36.08,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}世界で仆だけと知っていたかい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:39.75,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}この涙は 谁のものだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:43.38,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}仆のためか 君のためか
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:47.09,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}カラカラになってそれからまた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:50.72,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}谁かといたいと思えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:54.22,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.85,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}昨日までの梦のこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.85,0:23:01.77,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}魔法がとけたこの世界で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:05.19,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}仆は君を探したよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.40,0:23:08.90,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}Hello Hello 爱しい人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:12.49,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}君の声を闻かせてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.49,0:23:19.21,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)}梦の中でもう一度 连れていくよ
